### Anchor blockchain proof for a finalized transfer
POST http://localhost:8082/api/transfers/1/proof/anchor
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Read stored/computed transfer proof
GET http://localhost:8082/api/transfers/1/proof
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Verify current payload against stored hash and on-chain registry
GET http://localhost:8082/api/transfers/1/proof/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

